---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Styleguide · Clauderizer"
  description="Design tokens and primitives for the Clauderizer marketing site."
>
  <main class="container">
    <section class="intro">
      <p class="slug"><span class="no">Design system</span></p>
      <h1>A film about remembering.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        True-black ink, warm cream titles in Bodoni Moda, ember-gold memory light against cold steel
        amnesia. Every section is a scene.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="group">
      <h2>Colors</h2>
      <div class="swatches">
        <div class="swatch ink-900"><span>ink-900</span></div>
        <div class="swatch ink-800"><span>ink-800</span></div>
        <div class="swatch ink-700"><span>ink-700</span></div>
        <div class="swatch cream"><span>cream-50</span></div>
        <div class="swatch ember"><span>ember-400</span></div>
        <div class="swatch steel"><span>steel-400</span></div>
        <div class="swatch clay"><span>clay</span></div>
        <div class="swatch ok"><span>ok</span></div>
        <div class="swatch bad"><span>bad</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="group">
      <h2>Typography</h2>
      <p class="display">Display: Bodoni Moda, the film title.</p>
      <p class="display-italic">Display italic: the emotional beat.</p>
      <p class="body-large">Body large: for ledes and summaries.</p>
      <p>Body: standard paragraph text with good line-height.</p>
      <p class="mono">Mono: slug-lines, code, and terminal moments.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="group">
      <h2>Slug-lines & cuts</h2>
      <p class="slug"><span class="no">Scene 00</span> Int. repository - night</p>
      <p class="slug cold"><span class="no">Scene 00</span> The cold of forgetting</p>
      <hr class="flare" style="margin-top: 2rem" />
    </section>

    <section class="group">
      <h2>Buttons</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Primary</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#">Ghost</a>
        <button class="cmd" type="button" data-copy="uvx --from clauderizer clauderize init">
          <code><span class="prompt">$</span> uvx --from clauderizer clauderize init</code>
          <span class="copy-hint">copy</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="group">
      <h2>Motion</h2>
      <p>
        Reveals, parallax, Ken Burns, letterbox, and grain are motion-enhancements. Under
        <code>prefers-reduced-motion</code> all motion collapses and content is fully visible.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .intro {
    padding-block: clamp(5rem, 12vh, 8rem) 3rem;
  }
  .intro h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 6vw, 4.4rem);
  }
  .lede {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.35rem);
    color: var(--cream-200);
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
  }
  .group {
    padding-block: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--edge);
  }
  .group h2 {
    margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.4vw, 2.6rem);
  }

  .swatches {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(10rem, 1fr));
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  .swatch {
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--edge);
  }
  .swatch span {
    background: rgba(3, 4, 6, 0.65);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
  }
  .ink-900 {
    background: var(--ink-900);
    color: var(--cream-50);
  }
  .ink-800 {
    background: var(--ink-800);
    color: var(--cream-50);
  }
  .ink-700 {
    background: var(--ink-700);
    color: var(--cream-50);
  }
  .cream {
    background: var(--cream-50);
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .ember {
    background: var(--ember-400);
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .steel {
    background: var(--steel-400);
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .clay {
    background: var(--clay);
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .ok {
    background: var(--ok);
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .bad {
    background: var(--bad);
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }

  .display {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
    font-weight: 540;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    line-height: 1.02;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .display-italic {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4.4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 460;
    color: var(--ember-300);
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
  }
  .body-large {
    font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1.8vw, 1.25rem);
    color: var(--cream-200);
  }
  .mono {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--ember-400);
  }

  .row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.95em;
  }
</style>
